POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (09): AFGHANISTAN (WILD POLIOVIRUS), DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC OF CONGO (CIRCULATING VACCINE DERIVED POLIOVIRUS)
*******************************************************************************************************************************
